Key Match Events: Coby White and Zach LaVine finished the night with 33 points each.
Nikola Vucevic and Josh Giddey added double-doubles.
Josh Giddey threw an alley-oop pass to Lonzo Ball who finished it off with a dunk.
Miscellaneous Highlights: Lonzo Ball dunked the ball for the first time in three years in Chicago's previous game against the Washington Wizards.
The Bulls referenced Lonzo Ball's older brother, LiAngelo's, new song 'Tweaker' with the caption 'I MIGHT SWERVE BEND THAT CORNER WOAH.'
